<span class="score" id="comment_score_2062219">(<a href="reversethis-%7Bmoc.moclliw%7D%7Bta%7D%7B2so-yssas%7D" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 2062219); return false">スコア:0</a>)</span></h4>
